PEOPLE of the State of Michigan, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Eric Lynn BYRNES, Defendant-Appellant. SC: 157726
157727
COA: 341377
341380 Supreme Court of Michigan. February 4, 2019

Order

On order of the Court, the motion for reconsideration of this Court's September 12, 2018 order is considered, and it is DENIED, because it does not appear that the order was entered erroneously. The motion to correct clerical mistakes is DENIED.
